condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Article IV, 4.01 | Description :The Recipient has adopted the revised and updated Project Implementation Manualand Project Administrative, Financial and Accounting Manual, both in form and substance satisfactory to the Assn. | Due Date:23-Sep-2011
Finance Agreement :Article IV, 4.01 | Description :The Recipient has set up the Steering Committee by ArrêtE in a mannersatisfactory to the Association. | Due Date :23-Sep-2011

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. IV, B | Description :The Recipient shall not make withdrawals under components C1 and C2 of theProject until a Private Operator has been recruited and a Service Contract, acceptable to the Association, is in effect. | Due Date:30-Jun-2013

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, A | Description :Not later than 3 months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shallfinalize the transfer of the responsibility of the Recipient's urban water services to STE by Decree. | Due Date :30-Apr-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, B | Description :Not later than 9 months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shall enterinto a SC with a PO, and, at the same time, shall recruit the independent technical auditor of the SC. | Due Date :23-Nov-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, C | Description :Not later than 12 months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shalllaunch the study on water tariff and connection fee levels and the Recipient shall implement the recommendations. | Due Date:23-Feb-2013

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, D | Description :Not later than nine months after the Effective Date, the Recipient as soleshareholder of STE, shall have made its equity contribution to STE in full. | Due Date :31-Oct-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, E | Description :Not later than three months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shallenter into a delegation and performance contract with STE, in form and substance satisfactory to the Association. | Due Date:23-May-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, F | Description :Not later than 12 months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shall: (i)establish a mechanism for the automatic payment of the amounts owed to STE by other public institutions, and (ii) | Due Date:23-Feb-2013

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, G | Description :Not later than nine months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shallimplement a payment option scheme for its customers to enable payment of the connection fee in installments. | Due Date :23-Nov-2012

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sc. V, H | Description :Not later than 3 months after the Effective Date, the Recipient shall haveupdated the accounting software of the implementation unit for the purposes of the Project. | Due Date :23-May-2012
